{
  "text": "6 images/subject were selected for corneal nerve image analysis [CITATION_1] . All CCM images were analyzed using validated, purpose-written software (CCMetrics \u00ae , M. A. Dabbah, ISBE, University of Manchester, Manchester, UK) [CITATION_2] . Corneal nerve fiber density (CNFD) (no./mm 2 ), corneal nerve fiber branch density (CNBD) (no./mm 2 ) and corneal nerve fiber length (CNFL) (mm/mm 2 ) were manually quantified.",
